# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CODEOWNERS — auto-request review when matching files change.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones for the same path.
# Only list real GitHub accounts / teams; ghost references are silently
# ignored by GitHub and lead to "no reviewer ever requested" surprises.
# Consumers forking this repo should replace @YiWang24 with their own
# maintainer set.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Default — everything not matched below.
*                                       @YiWang24

# Workflow / action library — the heart of OpenCI; same owner for now.
/.github/                               @YiWang24
/.github/workflows/                     @YiWang24
/.github/scripts/                       @YiWang24
/actions/                               @YiWang24

# Prompt assets (treated specially: changes affect AI behaviour repo-wide).
/prompts/                               @YiWang24

# Documentation — SPEC must stay in sync with implementation.
/docs/                                  @YiWang24
/docs/SPEC.md                           @YiWang24
/README.md                              @YiWang24

# Security policy.
/SECURITY.md                            @YiWang24

# Manifest files — every SHA bump goes through code review.
/manifest.yml                           @YiWang24
/manifest-pending.yml                   @YiWang24

# Tests — change in lock-step with code under test.
/tests/                                 @YiWang24

# Tasks (implementation plan) — drive sequencing decisions.
/tasks/                                 @YiWang24
